# Read data

Import the data.
Data files are locally stored.

Import Aim 1: Exercise data

```{r}
L1 <- importDataToList("../data/raw/Ultragenyx Aim 1 combined.xlsx")
L1[["file"]]
L1[["nrow"]]
L1[["ncol"]]
L1[["names"]]
L1[["head"]]
D1 <- L1[["data"]]
```

```{r}
L2 <- importDataToList("../data/raw/Ultragenyx Aim 2 combined.xlsx")
L2[["file"]]
L2[["nrow"]]
L2[["ncol"]]
L2[["names"]]
L2[["head"]]
D2 <- L2[["data"]]
```


## Check data

Check the data.

```{r}
# tableChr(D1)
summary(D1$value)
summary(D2$value)
```
